\ltrch\fcs0 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe2057\cgrid\langnp2057\langfenp2057 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\ul\insrsid8738534\charrsid8738534 Information about interviewee
